        "message": "=={{`<div style=\"max-width:700px;margin:0 auto;background:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;color:#222222;\">  <div style=\"background:#000000;padding:32px 40px;text-align:center;\">    <h1 style=\"margin:0;color:#ffffff;font-size:24px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:3px;\">      APPLICATION UPDATE    </h1>  </div>  <div style=\"padding:50px 45px;line-height:1.8;font-size:15px;\">    <p style=\"margin-top:0;\">      Dear <strong>${$json.candidate_name || 'Applicant'}</strong>,    </p>    <p>      Thank you for your interest in the <strong>Junior Software Developer</strong> position and for taking the time to submit your application.    </p>    <p>      We appreciate the opportunity to review your qualifications, experience, and achievements.    </p>    <p>      We are pleased to inform you that your application has successfully passed our initial screening process.    </p>    <p>      Based on our evaluation, your profile demonstrates strong alignment with the requirements of the role and has been shortlisted for further consideration.    </p>    <p>      <strong>Evaluation Summary:</strong>    </p>    <p>      ${$json.reason || 'Your qualifications and experience demonstrated a strong match for the requirements of this position.'}    </p>    <p>      Our recruitment team will continue reviewing shortlisted candidates and will contact you regarding the next stage of the hiring process should your application be selected to move forward.    </p>    <p>      Thank you again for your interest in joining our organization. We appreciate the time and effort you invested in your application and look forward to the possibility of speaking with you further.    </p>    <div style=\"margin-top:40px;\">      <p style=\"margin-bottom:0;\">        Kind regards,      </p>      <p style=\"margin-top:5px;\">        <strong>Recruitment Team</strong><br>        Automated Resume Screening System      </p>    </div>    <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:50px;\">      <div style=\"        width:90px;        height:90px;        margin:0 auto;        border:2px solid #000000;        border-radius:50%;        line-height:90px;        font-size:42px;        font-weight:700;        color:#000000;        text-align:center;      \">        K      </div>    </div>  </div>  <div style=\"    border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;    background:#fafafa;    padding:20px;    text-align:center;    color:#666666;    font-size:12px;    letter-spacing:1.5px;  \">    CONGRATULATIONS ON ADVANCING TO THE NEXT STAGE  </div></div>`}}",
